 Testament texts.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aConduct of life. 0aWisdom. 4aBen Sira. 4aDeuterokanonische und zwischentestamentliche Literatur. 4aWeisheitsliteratur. 7aRELIGION / Biblical Criticism & Interpretation / Old Testament.2bisacsh  aBen Sira.  aDeuterocanonical and Intertestamentary Literature.  aWisdom Literature.1 aBeentjes, Pancratius C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCalduch-Benages, Nuria, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCorley, Jeremy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDiehl, Johannes Friedrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDiehl, Johannes, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEgger-Wenzel, Renate, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEgger-Wenzel, Renate, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEgo, Beate, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aElßner, Thomas R., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFeldmeier, Reinhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHieke, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKrammer, Ingrid, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNicklas, Tobias, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aReif, Stefan C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRitter-Müller, Petra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmitz, Barbara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchorch, Stefan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchöpflin, Karin, econtributo